title: Low prioity que VS 4am ranked ques going down
body: So basically my battery of my laptop is screwed which resulted in me afking for over 5 minutes for a couple of games before I figured out the actual issue. It is 3:41 in the morning. I have a 20 minute que timer. Does that mean that I wont be able to get in a ranked game or does that mean that I will be instantly que'd anyway? Please let me know.

replies.body: The name implies it is part of the queue.
Nvm I got my answer. You just fail to join que and waste 20 minutes of waiting.
